Uses of Package
com.ibm.itim.apps.workflow

Packages that use com.ibm.itim.apps.workflow
com.ibm.itim.apps.workflow Extends the com.ibm.itim.apps package to provide a remotable application programming interface for Workflow Process and Activity management. 
 

Classes in com.ibm.itim.apps.workflow used by com.ibm.itim.apps.workflow

          Provides management capabilities for an activity in a workflow process such as retrieving activity details, retrieving parent container process, retrieving assignments of this activity, completing activity asynchronously.
WorkflowAssignmentMO

WorkflowProcessMO

WorkflowResourceMO
